  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063450/extras/4dc3b8e403dd0d8768be2cc3cdac030d.avif?t=1729019772\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063450/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1729019772\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063450/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1729019772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063450/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1729019772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>An immersive experience made for you to rescue your tranquility, be inspired, relax and have fun!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063450/extras/c4dbc52223ac7c5676b3941df19a2351.poster.avif?t=1729019772\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063450/extras/c4dbc52223ac7c5676b3941df19a2351.webm?t=1729019772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>With the help of VR, we've perfected the immersion and relaxation experience of the first game!<br><br>Enter a world where stress will be left out! In an immersive and relaxing environment, forget about your worries by enchanting yourself and solving the puzzles and enjoy observing the power of life in nature!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063450/extras/f64d7582634d7493ad214018eb1b05f1.avif?t=1729019772\" width=584 height=287 />